      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0578P0-06644'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0578P0_19970304_GCR_114' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        5.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0578P0-06645'>
        <a name='S5LV0578P0_19970304_GCR_115'>  </a>
